WEBVTT

00:05:58.624 --> 00:06:02.615
the idea of countryfolk
as being without knowledge --

00:06:02.639 --> 00:06:05.121
these are ideas that historians
like me can go back,

00:06:05.145 --> 00:06:08.423
we can trace how
these stereotypes emerged.

00:06:08.447 --> 00:06:11.222
And they emerged at a time

00:06:12.555 --> 00:06:14.021
when Southeast Asia

00:06:15.379 --> 00:06:18.693
was being governed according to
the logic of colonial capitalism.

00:06:19.860 --> 00:06:21.717
And in so many ways,

00:06:22.725 --> 00:06:24.275
we've taken these ideas with us.

00:06:24.299 --> 00:06:25.824
They're part of us now.

00:06:25.848 --> 00:06:28.313
But we are not critical

00:06:28.337 --> 00:06:30.917
in interrogating ourselves
and asking ourselves,